		font-size: 12px;
		padding-top: 4px;
	}
	.show{visibility:visible;}
	#dragModal{
		background: #333;
		opacity: 0.6;
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;left: 0;right: 0;bottom: 0;
	}
	.nickname{padding-left: 5px;}
	.hide{display:none;}
	.topbar a{ color: #fff !important;}
	.globalnotice{ background: #F00; }
	.topbar{background: #555;color:#fff !important;font-size:75%;margin-bottom:5px;}
	.topbar div{padding:5px}
